<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich Forstmeister, Dekan zu St. Gangolf, und Georg von Löwenstein, Propst zu St. Jakob und Domherr zu Bamberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um (Anweisung des Georg von Löwenstein, Domherr zu Bamberg zur) Rücknahme der Klage gegen Hans Schürstab, Bürger zu Nürnberg, vor dem geistlichen Gericht und verweist auf den Rechtsweg zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_382" id="190r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_382_r1l19"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Heinrich <expan>Dechand<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l21">cʒu Tewrſtat </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_382_r1l22"><expan>Erwirdıg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> <expan>han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Schürſtab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l23">vnſer <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vvie Jr Jn von klag wegen 
<del rend="strikethrough">h </del> des Ervvirdigen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l24"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jörgen von Leoſtein <expan>Tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd p </del> cʒu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> v̈mb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l25">werltich ſache für ew auf geiſtlıch geriht geladen habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l26">vnd wir doch dem klager des rehten von dem <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l27"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> cʒehelffen ny <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſagt</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l28">klager <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> daran weiſen wöllet / daʒ Er von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l29">der klag laſʒ . Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc vnd het <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l30">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan></del> <expan>klag<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> icht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l31">vvir Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheinbote<ex>n</ex></expan> etc vt in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_382_r1l32"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jörgen von Leoſtein probſt cʒu ſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l33">Jacob vnd <expan>Tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des Stiftts ʒu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_382_r1l34"><expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> ſibi <expan>ip<ex>ſ</ex>i</expan> <expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> <expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_382" id="190r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Heinrich, <expan>dechand<ex>en</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen czu Tewrstat</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erwirdig<ex>er</ex></expan> und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat
                <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
<expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Schürstab, unser <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wie ir in
            von klag wegen des erwirdigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jörgen von Leostein,
                <expan>tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, ümb werltich
            sache für ew auf geistlich geriht geladen habt und wir doch dem klager des rehten von
            dem <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> cze helffen ny <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> klager <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> daran weisen wöllet, daz er von der klag lasz. Als etc.
            Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> der
                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>klag<ex>er</ex></expan> czu <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> icht <expan>cze sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbote<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jörgen von Leostein, probst czu sant Jacob und
                                <expan>tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des stiftts zu
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> sibi <expan>ip<ex>s</ex>i</expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
